{"tid":950963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（+1分）美起訴1中國人涉偷取石油公司商業機密","createTime":"2018-12-22T02:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T11:22:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9479e76b5fcc526c15247b1966c8db130779af56","tid":950963,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"美國司法部表示，一名持綠卡受僱美國一間石油公司的中國公民涉嫌盜取商業秘密，被拘捕並起訴。案件預計下星期三受審。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部的聲明指，一名於美國居住12年、35歲的中國公民，涉嫌於其工作的美國石油公司下載數以百計的檔案，涉及一項下游能源市場產品的製造資料，涉事貨品價值逾10億美元。調查發現他已獲一間中國公司聘用，懷疑他計畫以盜取得到的資料讓新僱主受益。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書提到他周四在俄克拉何馬州被捕後，即日提堂，將會於下周三初審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1394262/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1394262%2F&d=l9aZWPgK1g3ajVNLadFgEROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e5af97d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1394262%2F&h=93719921\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1394262/</a>"},{"pid":"f174957d42a95683c0ede06fd1c86ba3048d0d0a","tid":950963,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"5166a1724436b669b6628554296a3128cc48573c","tid":950963,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38219627d28a91991d5c6be8dd099ff23227f087","tid":950963,"uid":156090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"164比203"},{"pid":"4ee656b4ff5d4c2bf49df61c52d44e76313ee120","tid":950963,"uid":210842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5166a1724436b669b6628554296a3128cc48573c","tid":950963,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"若要人不知, 除非己莫為"},{"pid":"155ca2d181aff9086e5f86c7ff33baf9